data.name: Tutorial_Debts_Description
data.value:
Have you ever had issues with recovering your debts? Did you ever forget to pay off your debts?
Don't rely on your overwhelmed memory - let Debts take care of your finances!

data.name: Tutorial_Budget_Description
data.value:
Do you spend too much money on things you really do not need?
Start tracking your budget income and expenses with Debts!

data.name: Tutorial_PhoneContacts_Description
data.value:
Using Debts you can assign debt/loan to your contact - by picking phone number from contact list.
If your debtor install the Debts app through shared link - he will have instant access to detailed debt information.

data.name: Tutorial_GpsTracking_Description
data.value:
Can't recall where does it debt come from?
Have you borrowed some money from your friend and can't recall where and how?
No worries - we automatically fill place on map where you had added your finance operation!

data.name: Tutorial_NotifyDebtors_Description
data.value:
Your debtors don't take you seriously?
Inside the Debts you can send with an ease reminder through SMS or your messenger platform of choice!
Message will contain link which will lead your debtors to Debts app with further operation details.

data.name: Tutorial_More_Description
data.value:
Debts offer bunch of optional features that will help to organise your finances.
Notifications - get notifications about your debts/loans.
Rich search and filtering - filter or search your debts by date, name, contact and more!
Check it right now!
